snippet.title: The Making of Icarus | Episode 1 - Woodcutting Simulator
snippet.description:
What goes into making a AAA survival video game? In this first episode RocketWerkz CEO Dean Hall begins the story of Icarus' development over the last two years, starting from our very first milestone in 2019 - Woodcutting Simulator.

Subscribe and click the notification bell so you don't miss out on future episodes.

Wishlist Icarus on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1149460/ICARUS/
